CustomField.description: Groups related questions together for display (e.g., "Health Insurance", "Non-Cash Benefits"). When set, questions with the same group name will be displayed together in a card during interviews.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Optional: Group name for related fields. Questions with the same group name will display together in a card. Examples: Health Insurance, Non-Cash Benefits, Trauma Triggers, Warning Signs
CustomField.label: Field Set Group
